  schema:name "Ollama model tags" ;
  schema:description "Ollama identifies models with a `name:tag` syntax, where the name is the model family and the tag specifies the variant. For example, `qwen2.5:7b` means the Qwen 2.5 family at 7 billion parameters." ;
